summary: This document details the arrest of Alfredo Rodriguez on December 15, 2009, for Obstruction of Justice pursuant to a warrant issued by Magistrate Judge Linnea R. Johnson. Rodriguez was arrested at his West Palm Beach residence and transported to the Palm Beach County Jail.

keyFacts: Alfredo Rodriguez was arrested on December 15, 2009, for Obstruction of Justice (18 U.S.C. ยง 1512(c)).
The arrest warrant was issued by United States Magistrate Judge Linnea R. Johnson on December 8, 2009.
Rodriguez was arrested at his residence in West Palm Beach, Florida, and transported to the Palm Beach County Jail.
The arrest was made without incident by federal agents.
This document indicates an active obstruction of justice investigation related to the Epstein case in late 2009.
